content.text: I moved to a new apartment in East Austin. Still in Austin but different neighborhood. The rent is $2400/month for a 2-bedroom. Max loves the new yard.
Nice upgrade! East Austin is a great area. $2400 for a 2-bed with a yard for Max sounds reasonable for that neighborhood. How's the commute to DataFlow?
DataFlow is fully remote so no commute. That's one of the reasons I took the job. I do go into a coworking space sometimes though - WeWork on Congress Ave.
Remote work with an optional coworking spot is the sweet spot. WeWork on Congress Ave is a solid choice - good coffee shops nearby too. Best of both worlds.
